I have sons. We tried a new Thai restaurant. My sons are 10 and 7. I have a daughter who died last year when she was 12. I have a son who is 5. I like to garden with my sons. I also garden with my son. I read to my son. I used to read to my sons but they have grown out of it now.,"We did a bit of gardening together, did some chores around the house, and tried out a new Thai restaurant. My son is 5 and my daughter is forever 12. She died about a year ago. Well we don't have to talk about it if you're not comfortable with it. Are there any activities you like to do with your son, like I do gardening with my boys? Yeah, we do some gardening, but he gets bored quickly. Sometimes I read to him. We both like that. That really brings back memories of when I used to read to my boys. One day they had just grown out of it and I had to think of other ways to spend time with them. But I'll always treasure the nights we spent reading together. You can always suggest it to them again! My daughter and I had a several year period where we didn't read together too, but we picked it back up again the year before she passed.",test_850_3
