I have grandchildren. I like the beach. One of my grandchildren is 7 years old. I like picnics at the beach. I eat pork. I like pepperoni pizza best. I love ham and pineapple pizza.,"We went to the beach last weekend! It is a good thing to do with them because everyone can enjoy it at any age. I get that. Did you bring sandwiches? I love a picnic at the beach.  I have pulled pork in the slow cooker. I'm planning to have that with nice buns. It's too hot to cook.  That sounds delicious! I don't have any food, so I might just get a pizza. I love ham and pineapple. Most people hate it, but it is my favorite!",test_880_4
