I went to Michigan on a work trip. I like fishing. I've never been to Michigan. I eat fish. I have a wife and sons who also enjoy fishing. I work in sales. I work at a coffee shop. I have tattoos. My father is deceased.,"I was just in Michigan!  I was able to sneak away for a bit and get some fishing in caught a muskie I've never been to Michigan before. What type of fish is a muskie? Did you eat the muskie? the one I caught was about 30 pounds.  They have a mouth full of teeth.  Not really a tasty fish but they look mean No it was just me.  I wish they could come the whole family enjoys fishing.  My wife was shocked when I showed her a picture of the fish. Yea it was a sales convention but one day got canceled as there was a flood at the center so I was able to sneak away to fish.   That's great that you got a break and were able to pursue your personal interests for a day. I really could use a vacation from working at the coffee shop. However, I'm working double-shifts and overtime to save up for my next tattoo. I plan to get a portrait of my father's face next to the slogan I had tattooed on my chest in his memory.",test_905_2
