"I painted the butterflies in purple and blue. I recently completed a butterfly painting. I'd like to get a painting done of them. I enjoy drawing but I'm not a very talented artist myself. I own exotic pets, including a raccoon and a bearded dragon. The raccoon and the bearded dragon don't get along well. I have five pet dogs and three pet rats. I've never been paid to paint anything before. I work at a zoo. We have meerkats! I like to draw the animals when I'm on a break. The zoo animals are very friendly. I don't show the drawings to my colleagues. I really like meerkats. I think they would be fun animals to depict in a painting.","Would you like to see a butterfly painting I recently finished? I would love to! Painting butterflies, must take a lot of talent. What color are the butterflies in this painting? They're purple and blue. But oh thank you, I actually find them much easier subjects than other creatures. But if I had exotic pets like you I would be painting them all the time. Do you ever do art?  Oh no, you don't want to see my drawings! But what you said gives me an idea. Could I commission a painting of my bearded dragon and raccoon playing together? Oh no, not at all, that's why I think it would be so fun to have a painting of them playing together. You can be as creative as you want with it and I get a fun painting. It's a win win! Good old artistic license! But sure sounds great! You said you draw though, what do you like drawing? You don't have to show me, but perhaps I could swap my painting for a drawing of my five dogs and three rats?  I don't think I am any good, I like to doodle here and there, but I keep my drawings to myself. I can sure try to draw your dogs and rats, but you might hate it! I'm sure I'll love it. Do you draw animals from your work? If I had your job I would be constantly inspired, it might actually be too much inspiration lol  That is a really good guess! Many of the animals are so friendly they just let me sit there while they go about their day. I have a lot of doodles from when I am on break. I've thought about sharing them with my colleagues, but they might think it's weird. Oh I'm sure they'd love to see them. You should share them! But wow, I'm so jealous. Do you look after any meerkats? I'd love to paint meerkats. ",test_982_2
