ing on the sand more difficult? It might not be too expensive if you have people you can stay with so you don’t have to pay for a hotel.  I don’t have any trips planned but I would love to go to Greece. I've never been to Greece before, are you interested in the history? I've heard that there are lots of amazing things to see there. I've only ever been to Italy in Europe but I loved it.  I love learning about the Greek mythology!  I went to Italy when I was younger.  The food was amazing!",test_989_3
